			<div class="dablink">This article discusses utilitarian ethical theory. For a discussion of <a href="/wiki/John_Stuart_Mill" title="John Stuart Mill">John Stuart Mill</a>'s essay <i>Utilitarianism</i> (1861), see <a href="/wiki/Utilitarianism_(book)" title="Utilitarianism (book)">Utilitarianism (book)</a>.</div>
